🎯 CONSTRAINTS & SLA TARGETS

End-to-end latency target: <2.5 seconds (improved with Glow-TTS)

P99 latency: <3 seconds under peak load

Support thousands of concurrent calls with Kubernetes auto-scaling

Average call per-node capacity: 50-100 concurrent calls (t3.xlarge instance)

Auto-scale trigger: 70% CPU utilization or 80% memory

Noise robustness: Tested on 70-85 dB ambient field noise

Speech clarity: Weighted mean opinion score (MOS) > 3.8

Transcription accuracy: >85% for clean audio, >70% for noisy audio

High availability: 99.95% uptime (multi-region failover via Kamailio)

Security: End-to-end SRTP encryption, mutual TLS between services

Zero data retention option: Optional complete call purge after processing

🎯 FINAL GOAL

Deliver a fully open-source multilingual AI voice agent enabling:

Regional Language FOS ↔ Real-Time AI Translation ↔ Hinglish-speaking IT
Team ↔ Voice Reply translated back to regional language

No proprietary APIs. No paid services. Fully self-hosted.
